    {
      "id": "sybil_22_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_22",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. This unit has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for performance and safety. Featuring a documented service history and a well-preserved interior, this vehicle offers a sophisticated driving experience and remains a premier choice for the discerning buyer seeking consistent reliability and long-term value.",
