    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a new home. It\u2019s been super reliable and is in really solid shape\u2014perfect for your daily commutes or those fun weekend adventures! I\u2019ve truly loved driving this car, and it's been well-maintained so it's ready to hit the road the moment you hop in. Everything runs smoothly and it still looks great. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
