    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_23_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_23",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S54 straight-six featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS high-pressure stepless variable valve timing. The power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains tight, providing the communicative feedback and neutral handling balance this chassis is renowned for. Recent maintenance has prioritized mechanical longevity, including a subframe inspection and cooling system refresh. This is a mechanically honest, driver-centric example ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_3",
