    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hi there! I'm looking for a new owner for my awesome car! It\u2019s in really nice condition and has served me so well. It\u2019s reliable, drives great, and is just a solid all-around vehicle. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I think you\u2019re going to love how it handles. I'm pricing it to sell because I'd love to get it to its next owner soon. Drop me a message if you want to take a look\u2014I'm happy to chat and answer any questions you have!",
      "price": 28900.0,
